Claudine Auger https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claudine_Auger 0 Claudine Auger (born Claudine Oger; 26 April 1941) is a French actress best known for her role as Bond girl, Dominique "Domino" Derval, in the James Bond film Thunderball (1965). She earned the title of Miss France Monde and was also the first runner-up in the 1958 Miss World contest.
